@Phils Phindings
I've finished it twice Chrono Trigger and it's an excellent game in all its areas. Two years ago I started with Chrono Cross, played for a couple of hours but I didn't get hooked on the combat system and stopped playing it. 

I never knew if it's really as good as they say and maybe I have a very closed mind, perhaps I'll try again and see if I can enjoy the game and especially the combat system.
